        "logic": "var calc_output = [];\n\nvar is = parseFloat(is);\nvar rr = parseFloat(rr);\nvar nps = parseFloat(nps);\nvar cough = parseFloat(cough);\n\nvar score = is + rr + nps + cough;\n\nvar risk;\nif (score == 0) {\n    risk = 'Low';\n} else if (score <= 2) {\n    risk = 'Intermediate';\n} else if (score <= 4) {\n    risk = 'High';\n}\n\ncalc_output.push({\n    name: 'mini',\n    value: score,\n    value_text: 'points',\n    message: risk + ' risk of ≥1 adverse outcome'\n});\ncalc_output.push({\n    name: '10486_SCARF Score_result',\n    value: score,\n    value_text: 'points',\n    message: 'SCARF Score'\n});\ncalc_output.push({\n    name: '10486_SCARF Score_interpretation',\n    value: risk,\n    value_text: 'risk',\n    message: 'Risk of ≥1 adverse outcome'\n});",
